  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/66b76c8b00067df0f4203dee522aa43b.avif?t=1742177300\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leshy and the Magic Book are on a quest to unlock <strong>ancient animal powers,</strong> but the <strong>Red Panda Temple</strong> <strong>is overrun by slimes!</strong> Help Leshy crush the slime invasion and restore peace!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/0c0c0d76c094e15cab7d23107fff0d72.avif?t=1742177300\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras_big/0c0c0d76c094e15cab7d23107fff0d72.avif?t=1742177300 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・Slime-Slaying Frenzy!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive 15 minutes of non-stop slime smashing chaos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge exploding blobs, weave through bullet-hell madness, and conquer the ultimate slime overlord!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/1de85267d8299b84e763c97794d7fc6e.avif?t=1742177300\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・Leshy's Magic Arsenal!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness elemental magic—<strong>Fire, ice, electricity, wind</strong> <strong>and more!</strong> Mix and match spells to create <strong>your own killer skill set</strong> and wipe out those gooey invaders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/9a5c5d1a0772cb5944f43671cf8bf224.avif?t=1742177300\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras_big/9a5c5d1a0772cb5944f43671cf8bf224.avif?t=1742177300 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・Game-Changing Runes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boost Leshy's power with <strong>legendary runes!</strong> Spend hard-earned gold on <strong>epic buffs</strong>, then <strong>discover hidden upgrade shops</strong> to make them even stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/66b76c8b00067df0f4203dee522aa43b.avif?t=1742177300\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leshy and the Magic Book are on a quest to unlock <strong>ancient animal powers,</strong> but the <strong>Red Panda Temple</strong> <strong>is overrun by slimes!</strong> Help Leshy crush the slime invasion and restore peace!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/0c0c0d76c094e15cab7d23107fff0d72.avif?t=1742177300\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras_big/0c0c0d76c094e15cab7d23107fff0d72.avif?t=1742177300 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・Slime-Slaying Frenzy!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive 15 minutes of non-stop slime smashing chaos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge exploding blobs, weave through bullet-hell madness, and conquer the ultimate slime overlord!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/1de85267d8299b84e763c97794d7fc6e.avif?t=1742177300\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・Leshy's Magic Arsenal!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness elemental magic—<strong>Fire, ice, electricity, wind</strong> <strong>and more!</strong> Mix and match spells to create <strong>your own killer skill set</strong> and wipe out those gooey invaders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366910/extras/9a5c5d1a0772cb5